Class TCGAUtilities

public class TCGAUtilities
extends java.lang.Object

org.systemsbiology.tcga.TCGAUtilities written by Steve Lewis on Apr 9, 2010 28 letters : TCGA-nn-nnnn-nna-nna-nnnn-nn in order from left-to-right : nn = tissue collection site ID (two digit integer) nnnn = patient ID (4 digits) nn = sample type (01 = tumor, 10 = blood, 11 = adjacent tissue) a = vial nn = portion a = analyte nnnn = plate (4 digits) nn = analysis center (where the sample was processed and the data generated)
